frames.caption: A man and a woman walk hand in hand towards a dramatic horizon, where fiery orange and cool blue skies meet. A crack in the ground glows with molten light, dividing the scene into two contrasting halves.
frames.description: The scene depicts a surreal landscape where a couple walks towards a horizon split by fire and storm. The left side is engulfed in fiery orange clouds, while the right is dominated by dark blue storm clouds with lightning. The ground beneath them is cracked, glowing with a fiery light.
